<item>
            <title>[LU-9447] Need explicit check for 2 arg ib_alloc_pd for SLES 12 SP3</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9447</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The fix for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9026&quot; title=&quot;Adapt to the removal of ib_get_dma_mr()&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-9026&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-9026&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; addresses two API changes with a single autoconf check. The changes are:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;commit ed082d36a7b2c27d1cda55fdfb28af18040c4a89
Author: Christoph Hellwig &amp;lt;hch@lst.de&amp;gt;
Date:   Mon Sep 5 12:56:17 2016 +0200

    IB/core: add support to create a unsafe global rkey to ib_create_pd

commit 5ef990f06bd7e3cf521b5705d898d8e43d04ea90
Author: Christoph Hellwig &amp;lt;hch@lst.de&amp;gt;
Date:   Mon Sep 5 12:56:21 2016 +0200

    IB/core: remove ib_get_dma_mr
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The current SLES 12 SP3 beta has that first commit, &quot;ed082d36a7&quot;, but not the second one. I propose to introduce an explicit check for the ib_alloc_pd() function with two arguments. I have a patch and will push it soon.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
